\cb3 ## \uc0\u9989  Acceptance Criteria (Checklist format, binary pass/fail)\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Core Layout Functionality\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] Viewport is fixed at `100dvh` - app frame never grows beyond screen height\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] Main content area scrolls internally with `overflow-y: auto`\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] `overscroll-behavior: contain` prevents scroll-chaining to parent/body\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] Mobile Safari address bar doesn't cause layout jumps or white space\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Sticky Headers\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] Master Availability Grid headers remain sticky while scrolling player names\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] Sticky headers have proper z-index stacking (headers above content)\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] Headers maintain background color/opacity when scrolled\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] Horizontal scrolling works correctly with sticky left column\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Mobile UX\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] No scroll-chaining when modals (Edit Player) are open\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] Safe area insets respected on iOS (notch/home indicator)\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] Touch scrolling feels native with momentum and rubber-banding\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] Address bar hide/show doesn't break layout\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ### Integration\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] All existing pages (Roster, Grid, Board, DepthChart) work without regression\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] Sidebar navigation functions correctly\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] Modal/dialog components open without scroll issues\cb1 \
\cb3 - [ ] Performance: No layout thrashing or jank during scrolling\cb1 \
\
\cb3 ## \uc0\u9888 \u65039  Edge Cases (Already Handled)\cb1 \
\cb3 1. **Mobile Safari 100vh bug** - Using `100dvh` instead of `100vh` handles dynamic viewport\cb1 \
\cb3 2. **Scroll-chaining prevention** - `overscroll-behavior: contain` on scroll containers\cb1 \
\cb3 3. **Z-index conflicts** - Proper stacking context for sticky headers vs modals\cb1 \
\cb3 4. **Safe area insets** - Already implemented in Layout.tsx for iOS notch\cb1 \
\cb3 5. **Browser support** - Fallbacks for browsers that don't support `100dvh` or `overscroll-behavior`\cb1 \
